headline: Huntington Bancshares to Host Investor Day on February 6, 2025
summary: Huntington Bancshares Incorporated (Nasdaq: HBAN) will host an Investor Day in New York City on Thursday, February 6, 2025. Presentations will be given by chairman, president and chief executive officer, Stephen Steinour and members of Huntington's management team. Attendance in person is by invitation only to institutional investors and analysts. Presentations are expected to begin at 8:30 a.m. ET and to conclude at approximately 1 p.m. ET.
